\n}\n\nfinal class LineNumbersSampleClass\n\ntrait LineNumbersSerializableCallable extends Callable[String] with Serializable\n"}
[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Exploring Java lambda class**\n\nI'm considering how the lambda class will be hidden at runtime, which is a good thing. If it's not, the anonymous class would have a .class resource and use the getStreamForClass method. This means that some dynamic reflection call sites for lambdas might not be properly covered. I guess I need a stronger approach to get the Java lambda. I could potentially add a Java test source to explore this further.\n\n**Exploring Scala and Java Interoperability**\n\nI'm wondering about the Java interface Runnable in the context of Scala's trait system. Should I consider using Java's `java.util.concurrent.Callable[String]` with `Serializable`? There’s a thought about intersections and how Scala SAM might convert to that intersection type. I need to think about the implications of using `LambdaMetafactory` as an alternative. It’s interesting to explore how these different components fit together!\n\n**Evaluating native assertions**\n\nI’m considering if the `NoSourceInfo` assertion is suitable for native elements before the metadata stage. I realize that testing will be essential to generate metadata. Initially, I feel uncertain about using it for natives. Also, I’m exploring the idea of whether the classloader should be null; it seems no there. It’s apparent that the Native Image UnsupportedFeatureError for lambda isn't applicable since it doesn’t involve dynamic class loading after the build. Now I just need to create a file.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0f86c62bcc67044e0169fb15bb00548190bf3d927aaa79b08a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp-xXPMKObW96P8dvtmuKJaUpdlp1-n5T_i8mtIYms2jphbWco4aK3IPk1LOw82b7mq-HKku6NAWi2GUh35U_BQPOSp5d_tBGV2if6cmjsmjfiSB2cZFjXOhanY_4qOrQ9BnK86ELD5FSqgiIQPBqT5oAg6xFszSseaLjQozfbTL8JFKdfb0ysMvYRUINHJ7BaNM9uWahHOwr-zpPtKtIywO5EgX5WjvPD7jgA9M2tlTlyVcnseRPPe4kf6--hLhrYLa_v14pqt_pkzJU